{"tid":1807971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水警警司彭歐陽國基疑家中猝死","createTime":"2020-01-02T05:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","uid":230104,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc13e1058cde36ae9820b0bae2007e9c8a2cdff","tid":1807971,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"2016/11/15<br />\n<br />\n水警總區總部的歐陽國基警司今午疑因病發猝死家中，終年53歲。據悉，他昨日因心臟不適請病假看醫生，今日應如常上班，惟同袍未見他，於是到鯉景灣怡昌閣住所了解，惟無人應門，報警破門入屋，發現他倒在廳中的沙發上明顯死亡，毋須送院。經初步調查後，認為死因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n他現於水警總區總部做行政，負責人事部工作。警員及後安排仵工將其遺體舁送殮房，稍後剖屍確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n歐陽國基於香港大學畢業後加入警隊，已婚，事發時妻子正在外國。他自少喜歡中國武術，1982年開始習武，先後接觸中外不同派別的武術，樂此不疲，現為香港警察中國武術會會長，本周日（13日）他還在尖沙咀九龍公園表演，他在Facebook留言「這是最後一次以會長身份於功夫閣表演武術」。"},{"pid":"0dd92c6ee69d00109072028aa2e199dda58bdae0","tid":1807971,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c39a33818919e605e125afbd510c1c4d0fa6e6a","tid":1807971,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a987d6969c787bbfdaaf58b30e73ecabaab4b45e","tid":1807971,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240cf3ec3ea8bff64a6cb18e49c770bf4d5ecd51","tid":1807971,"uid":31787,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 依家2020啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8a238299ad0c72ab66d0c3dea34a7b50b6d426","tid":1807971,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"